lead_paragraph: Gamblers wagered a record $132.5 million at Nevada casinos on Super Bowl 50 with an upset win for the Denver Broncos over the Carolina Panthers giving sportsbooks their highest profit in two years on the NFL showpiece.

headline.print_headline: Super Bowl Fans Bet Record $132.5 Million at Nevada Casinos
